Class NetmonAdapter

java.lang.Object
  com.att.aro.pcap.NetmonAdapter

public class NetmonAdapter
extends java.lang.Object

Encapsulates the logic used for parsing data from a Microsoft Network Monitor trace file and adapting it for use with the ARO Data Analyzer.
